section.title: Detailed Description
section.para: CMSIS Cortex-M3 Device Peripheral Access Layer Header File. This file contains all the peripheral register's definitions, bits definitions and memory mapping for STM32F1xx devices.

Author
MCD Application Team
This file contains:
Data structures and the address mapping for all peripherals
Peripheral's registers declarations and bits definition
Macros to access peripherals registers hardware
